  "content": "Synergy refers to the interaction or cooperation of two or more agents to produce an effect that is greater than the sum of their individual contributions. In a business context, synergy can be achieved through strategic partnerships or mergers. Sample sentence: 'The partnership between Kodansha and the new publishing company created a synergy that increased their market share significantly.'",
